 <p> Here at Ted's Battle Bear Emporium, we run an online marketlpace were people can buy and sell thier ursine machines of destruction.  We are an international outfit, so we are able to get our hands on all various makes and models from across the world!(Whats left of it at least.) Click below to view what we currently have in our inventory!</p>
